<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="worthwhile-adj">worthwhile <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌwɜːθ'waɪl/    美 /ˌwɜːrθ'waɪl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>值得花时间 / 精力的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>worthwhile</strong> job
值得做的工作</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The smile on her face made it all worthwhile. 
她脸上的笑容使得这一切都很值得。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We decided to give the money to a worthwhile cause(=one that helps people).
我们决定把这笔钱投入到高尚的事业中。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>it is worthwhile doing / to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It is worthwhile comparing / to compare prices.
有必要比较一下价格。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Mistakes don’t just happen; they occur for a reason. Find out the reason, and then making the mistake becomes <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (值得的).   （2010 湖北改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. worthwhile  </p></div>